Revision history for Perl extension Mobile::P2kMoto.

0.03
	- Fixed the simple filehandle interface to close-on-destroy
	  like normal Perl filehandles.

0.02  Sun Sep  9 19:40:27 CEST 2007
	- Added easy_openPhone() as a simplified interface
	  to (auto)configuration, P2K mode setting and opening
	  the phone.
	- Added dir() as a simplified and more powerful interface to
	  searchRequest/fileList.
	- Fixed open() and read() to actually work.
	- Added a simplified interface for opening/reading/writing files.
	- Added a simple command line P2K client.

0.01  Tue Jun 26 21:10:14 CEST 2007
	- Initial release
